---
description: FeedFoundry product doctrine
alwaysApply: true
---

FeedFoundry is a creator archive intelligence engine.

Never implement URL ingestion in V1. All jobs begin from uploaded files.

The output set is:
- Transcript
- Clean transcript
- Chapters
- Clip candidates
- Show notes
- Metadata
- CTAs
- Fact Sheet
- FAQs
- Hosted Manifest
- Export bundle

The business model is annual access/hosting plus processing credits, not classic monthly SaaS.

Use clear schemas, explicit job states, and strict AI cost controls.
